    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>Sleepy Heroes</strong>中，您可以尝试在每个回合中创造最佳协同效应。您可以像解谜一样通过排序卡牌来完成每轮游戏，并与昏昏欲睡的生物对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/8af8313a94297c849a2cfcd32c2e0d2e.poster.avif?t=1727424352\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/8af8313a94297c849a2cfcd32c2e0d2e.webm?t=1727424352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/8af8313a94297c849a2cfcd32c2e0d2e.mp4?t=1727424352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >就像解谜一样！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在自动战斗类的对战中，您可以利用按顺序排列卡牌的特殊机制，坐下来放松一下。在<strong>Sleepy Heroes</strong>中，出牌顺序非常重要。把握这一独创机制，创造出精彩的连击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/9a7f466e9cb7c97b497eff348f0889c4.poster.avif?t=1727424352\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/9a7f466e9cb7c97b497eff348f0889c4.webm?t=1727424352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/9a7f466e9cb7c97b497eff348f0889c4.mp4?t=1727424352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每场战斗中，选择临时卡牌并尝试使用。赢得一场战斗后，再添加永久卡牌，从而建立自己的战略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用数十种不同的小饰品来强化你的卡组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在活动和商店中做出选择。击败强大的精英，到达最后的BOSS。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受Lo-Fi音乐，反复发掘不同的协同效果。</p>",
